Run the below cmds in the terminal
$ sudo apt update
$ sudo apt install
$ sudo install pip 
$ sudo pip install flask

Run 
$ python app.py
to run flask --- Webserver on local IP:5000 (port- 5000)

Imp note 
*Dont alter the directories *
